ESC - Closes Maze application
LEFT CTRL - Toggles between mouse mode and keyboard only mode.

All modes:
W - Move forward
S - Move backward
SHIFT - Hold to sprint.
Z - To crouch/stand.
TAB - Open Minimap.

Mouse mode:
Rotate camera using the mouse.
A - Move laterally left.
D - Move laterally right.

Keyboard only mode:
A - Rotate camera left.
D - Rotate camera right.
